    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Log Query Examples",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "content": "# Log Query Examples\n\n## Basic Queries\n````\n# All Pinjol logs (container + file)\n{platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"} or {job=\"pinjol\"}\n\n# Error logs only\n{platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"} | json | level=\"error\" or {job=\"pinjol\", level=\"error\"}\n\n# Search for database patterns\n{platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"} |~ \"(?i)database\" or {job=\"pinjol\"} |~ \"(?i)database\"\n````\n\n## Advanced Queries\n````\n# Count errors by minute\ncount_over_time({platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"} | json | level=\"error\" [1m]) or count_over_time({job=\"pinjol\", level=\"error\"} [1m])\n\n# Search for specific patterns\n{platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"} |~ \"loan.*created\" or {job=\"pinjol\"} |~ \"loan.*created\"\n\n# Filter by service name\n{platform=\"docker\", service_name=\"pinjol-app\"}\n````\n\n## Useful Patterns\n- `|~ \"(?i)error\"` - Case insensitive error search\n- `| json` - Parse JSON logs from containers\n- `| line_format \"{{.message}}\"` - Format output\n- `+= \"field\"` - Add field to output\n- `{platform=\"docker\"}` - Container logs\n- `{job=\"system\"}` - System logs",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 40
      }
    }
